<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <% if (column) { %>
    <title><%= column.seo_title || column.title %> | TONE'S CLINIC 명동점 칼럼</title>
    <meta name="description" content="<%= column.seo_desc || column.content.replace(/<[^>]*>/g, '').substring(0, 160) %>">
    <meta property="og:title" content="<%= column.seo_title || column.title %>">
    <meta property="og:description" content="<%= column.seo_desc || column.content.replace(/<[^>]*>/g, '').substring(0, 160) %>">
    <meta property="og:type" content="article">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://tones-myeongdong.com/column/<%= column.slug %>">
    <% if (column.thumbnail) { %>
      <meta property="og:image" content="https://tones-myeongdong.com<%= column.thumbnail %>">
    <% } %>
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://tones-myeongdong.com/column/<%= column.slug %>">
    <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "Article",
      "headline": "<%= column.title %>",
      "author": { "@type": "Person", "name": "<%= column.author %>" },
      "datePublished": "<%= column.created_at %>",
      "dateModified": "<%= column.updated_at %>",
      "publisher": {
        "@type": "Organization",
        "name": "TONE'S CLINIC 명동점"
      }
    }
    </script>
  <% } else { %>
    <title>칼럼을 찾을 수 없습니다 | TONE'S CLINIC 명동점</title>
  <% } %>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">

  <style>
    .column-detail {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 120px 24px 80px;
    }

    .column-detail__category {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #7C7559;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .column-detail__category a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .column-detail__category a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .column-detail h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #5C2A2E;
      line-height: 1.4;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .column-detail__meta {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #999;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      padding-bottom: 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .column-detail__meta span {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .column-detail__thumbnail {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .column-detail__thumbnail img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    .column-detail__content {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: #444;
      word-break: keep-all;
    }

    .column-detail__content h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #5C2A2E;
      margin: 40px 0 16px;
    }

    .column-detail__content h3 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #5C2A2E;
      margin: 32px 0 12px;
    }

    .column-detail__content p {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .column-detail__content img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .column-detail__content blockquote {
      border-left: 3px solid #DDCDBB;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      margin: 24px 0;
      background: #FAFAF9;
      color: #666;
      border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
    }

    .column-detail__content ul,
    .column-detail__content ol {
      padding-left: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .column-detail__content li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .column-detail__content a {
      color: #5C2A2E;
      text-decoration: underline;
      text-underline-offset: 3px;
    }

    /* Author Bio */
    .author-bio {
      margin-top: 48px;
      padding: 28px;
      background: #F5F3EF;
      border-radius: 8px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .author-bio__avatar {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #5C2A2E;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #DDCDBB;
      font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
      font-size: 24px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .author-bio__info h4 {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #5C2A2E;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .author-bio__info p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #888;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* Related */
    .related-section {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px 80px;
    }

    .related-section h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #5C2A2E;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      padding-top: 40px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }

    .related-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .related-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .related-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }

    .related-card__thumb {
      width: 100%;
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
      background: #f0ece6;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .related-card__thumb img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .related-card__thumb .no-thumb {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #ccc;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .related-card__body {
      padding: 14px;
    }

    .related-card__title {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #5C2A2E;
      line-height: 1.5;
      display: -webkit-box;
      -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
      -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .related-card__date {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #bbb;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    /* Back link */
    .column-back {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 24px 60px;
    }

    .column-back a {
      color: #999;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 14px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }

    .column-back a:hover {
      color: #5C2A2E;
    }

    /* Not found */
    .not-found {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 120px 20px;
    }

    .not-found h1 {
      font-size: 48px;
      opacity: 0.2;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .not-found p {
      color: #999;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .not-found a {
      color: #5C2A2E;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .column-detail {
        padding-top: 80px;
      }

      .column-detail h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .related-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .author-bio {
        flex-direction: column;
        text-align: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="header" id="header">
    <div class="header__inner">
      <a href="/" class="header__logo">
        <span class="header__logo-main">TONE'S CLINIC</span>
        <span class="header__logo-sub">MYEONGDONG</span>
      </a>
      <nav class="header__nav" id="nav">
        <ul class="header__menu">
          <li><a href="/" class="header__link">HOME</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about.html" class="header__link">소개</a></li>
          <li class="header__has-dropdown">
            <a href="/treatments/" class="header__link">시술안내</a>
            <ul class="header__dropdown">
              <li><a href="/treatments/lifting.html">리프팅</a></li>
              <li><a href="/treatments/skincare.html">피부관리</a></li>
              <li><a href="/treatments/injection.html">주사시술</a></li>
              <li><a href="/treatments/body.html">체형관리</a></li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li><a href="/results.html" class="header__link">전후사진</a></li>
          <li><a href="/column/" class="header__link active">칼럼</a></li>
          <li><a href="/location.html" class="header__link">오시는 길</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
      <div class="header__actions">
        <a href="/reservation.html" class="header__cta">예약하기</a>
        <button class="header__hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="메뉴 열기">
          <span></span><span></span><span></span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <% if (!column) { %>
    <div class="not-found">
      <h1>404</h1>
      <p>요청하신 칼럼을 찾을 수 없습니다.</p>
      <a href="/column/">칼럼 목록으로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>
  <% } else { %>

    <article class="column-detail">
      <% if (column.category_name) { %>
        <span class="column-detail__category">
          <a href="/column/category/<%= column.category_slug %>"><%= column.category_name %></a>
        </span>
      <% } %>

      <h1><%= column.title %></h1>

      <div class="column-detail__meta">
        <span><%= column.author %></span>
        <span><%= new Date(column.created_at).toLocaleDateString('ko-KR', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' }) %></span>
        <span><%= Math.max(1, Math.ceil(column.content.replace(/<[^>]*>/g, '').length / 500)) %>분 읽기</span>
      </div>

      <% if (column.thumbnail) { %>
        <div class="column-detail__thumbnail">
          <img src="<%= column.thumbnail %>" alt="<%= column.title %>">
        </div>
      <% } %>

      <div class="column-detail__content">
        <%- column.content %>
      </div>

      <!-- Author Bio -->
      <div class="author-bio">
        <div class="author-bio__avatar">DA</div>
        <div class="author-bio__info">
          <h4><%= column.author %></h4>
          <p>TONE'S CLINIC 명동점 전문의. 환자 한 분 한 분의 피부 고민에 진심으로 다가가며, 최신 피부과학에 기반한 정확한 정보를 전해드립니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- Related Columns -->
    <% if (related.length > 0) { %>
      <section class="related-section">
        <h2>관련 칼럼</h2>
        <div class="related-grid">
          <% related.forEach(rel => { %>
            <a href="/column/<%= rel.slug %>" class="related-card">
              <div class="related-card__thumb">
                <% if (rel.thumbnail) { %>
                  <img src="<%= rel.thumbnail %>" alt="<%= rel.title %>" loading="lazy">
                <% } else { %>
                  <div class="no-thumb">DA</div>
                <% } %>
              </div>
              <div class="related-card__body">
                <h3 class="related-card__title"><%= rel.title %></h3>
                <span class="related-card__date"><%= new Date(rel.created_at).toLocaleDateString('ko-KR') %></span>
              </div>
            </a>
          <% }); %>
        </div>
      </section>
    <% } %>

    <div class="column-back">
      <a href="/column/">&larr; 칼럼 목록으로 돌아가기</a>
    </div>

  <% } %>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div class="footer__inner">
      <div class="footer__top">
        <div class="footer__brand">
          <div class="footer__logo">
            <span class="footer__logo-main">TONE'S CLINIC</span>
            <span class="footer__logo-sub">MYEONGDONG</span>
          </div>
          <p class="footer__desc">서울 명동에 위치한 프리미엄 피부과<br>TONE'S CLINIC 명동점입니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer__links">
          <div class="footer__col">
            <h4>시술안내</h4>
            <a href="/treatments/lifting.html">리프팅</a>
            <a href="/treatments/skincare.html">피부관리</a>
            <a href="/treatments/injection.html">주사시술</a>
            <a href="/treatments/body.html">체형관리</a>
          </div>
          <div class="footer__col">
            <h4>병원안내</h4>
            <a href="/about.html">병원소개</a>
            <a href="/results.html">전후사진</a>
            <a href="/column/">칼럼</a>
          </div>
          <div class="footer__col">
            <h4>고객지원</h4>
            <a href="/reservation.html">예약하기</a>
            <a href="/location.html">오시는 길</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer__bottom">
        <div class="footer__info">
          <p>디에이피부과의원 명동점 | 대표: OOO | 사업자등록번호: XXX-XX-XXXXX</p>
          <p>서울특별시 중구 명동길 [상세주소] | 대표전화: 02-XXXX-XXXX</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer__legal">
          <a href="/privacy.html">개인정보처리방침</a>
          <a href="/terms.html">이용약관</a>
        </div>
        <p class="footer__copy">&copy; 2026 TONE'S CLINIC MYEONGDONG. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
